<lb n="0550a17"/><head>No. 743</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0550a18"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說<note n="0550007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忠＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忠＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550007"><lem>忠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app>心經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0550a19"/>
<lb n="0550a20"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="0550008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550008"><lem>天竺三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0550a21"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。<note n="0550009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（是）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（是）＋時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550009"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0550a22"/>諸菩薩。四輩弟子。天龍鬼神。帝王<note n="0550010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">臣＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550010"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民。日
<lb n="0550a23"/>會聽經。佛右面比丘。名曰目連。神通妙達。智
<lb n="0550a24"/>如虛空。隨時變化。權智並行。普<note n="0550011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＝為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550011"><lem>還</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為</rdg></app>濟眾。數
<lb n="0550a25"/>如&M010527;沙。諸天稽首。靡不師仰。佛告目連。彼有
<lb n="0550a26"/>大國。去斯八千。處在邊境。不&CB00418;三尊之至
<lb n="0550a27"/>靈。希聞如來無所著正真等<note n="0550012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔正〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔正〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550012"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>覺神妙清化。
<lb n="0550a28"/>習於顛倒眾邪之行。以為真諦。王及臣民。奉
<lb n="0550a29"/>事梵志等五百人。各有五通<note n="0550013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔力〕－【宮】</note><app n="0550013"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。能移山<note n="0550014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝駐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝駐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550014"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">駐</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0743.0550b" n="0550b"/>
<lb n="0550b01"/>流。分身變化。國有大山。塞民逕路。舉國患之。
<lb n="0550b02"/>王以山為民艱難。具向梵志說之。梵志答曰。
<lb n="0550b03"/>吾等自為民除<note n="0550015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">害＝患【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">害＝患【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550015"><lem>害</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">患</rdg></app>。王無慼焉。即繞山坐。各
<lb n="0550b04"/>一其心。以道定力。山起欲移。佛告目連。汝往
<lb n="0550b05"/>彼國。現道神化。長度梵志。濟其<note n="0550016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">君＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">君＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550016"><lem>君</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>民。令遠
<lb n="0550b06"/>三塗。永處福堂。目連受教。承佛威神。尋路放
<lb n="0550b07"/>光。遏絕日明。懸處虛空。當其山<note n="0550017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">巔＝頂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">巔＝頂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550017"><lem>巔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">頂</rdg></app>。山為不
<lb n="0550b08"/>動。梵志驚曰。此山已起。誰<note n="0550018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迴＝遏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迴＝遏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550018"><lem>迴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">遏</rdg></app>之乎。日又無
<lb n="0550b09"/>光。此將有<note n="0550019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝異【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝異【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550019"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">異</rdg></app>。中有<note n="0550020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝邪【宮】</note><app n="0550020"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>者。<note n="0550021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＋（道）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＋（道）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550021"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以道</rdg></app>定意觀眾弟
<lb n="0550b10"/>子心。誰穢濁者。令山不移。&CB00418;見<note n="0550022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝其【宮】</note><app n="0550022"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">其</rdg></app>心。普有
<lb n="0550b11"/>道淨。國榮寶色。不穢其心。仰頭觀見。&CB00418;一沙
<lb n="0550b12"/>門。當其山上。梵志僉曰。正是瞿曇弟子所為。
<lb n="0550b13"/>梵志呼曰。王令吾等為民除患。汝抑之為。目
<lb n="0550b14"/>連答曰。吾自懸虛。誰抑汝<note n="0550023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔等〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔等〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550023"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>山。梵志三<note n="0550024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＝進【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡＝進【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550024"><lem>盡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">進</rdg></app>
<lb n="0550b15"/>道力。欲令山移。山<note n="0550025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝又【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入＝又【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550025"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>三下。遂成平地。梵志
<lb n="0550b16"/>顧相謂曰。夫有明達。道德深者。即吾等師。咸
<lb n="0550b17"/>興<note n="0550026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">整＝正【三】，政【宮】</note><note n="0550026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">整＝正【宋】【元】【明】，＝政【宮】</note><app n="0550026"><lem>整</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">正</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">政</rdg></app>服。稽首敬白。願為弟子。示吾極<note n="0550027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聖＝靈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聖＝靈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550027"><lem>聖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">靈</rdg></app>。目
<lb n="0550b18"/>連答曰。汝等欲去瞑就明者善。吾有尊師。
<lb n="0550b19"/><note n="0550028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">號＋（曰）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">號＋（曰）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550028"><lem>號</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">號曰</rdg></app>無上正真天中之天。為一切智。汝等尋吾
<lb n="0550b20"/>往至佛所。<note n="0550029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸梵志＝梵志答【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸梵志＝梵志答【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550029"><lem>諸梵志</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">梵志答</rdg></app>曰。佛之導化。寧<note n="0550030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殊＝踰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殊＝踰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550030"><lem>殊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">踰</rdg></app>於師
<lb n="0550b21"/>乎。目連曰佛以須彌為芥子。吾以芥子為須
<lb n="0550b22"/>彌。歎佛德畢曰。汝等尋吾後。目連接諸梵志。
<lb n="0550b23"/>猶若壯士屈伸臂頃。即在佛前。具陳其情。白
<lb n="0550b24"/>佛言。吾承無上正真<note n="0550031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔神勢〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔神勢〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550031"><lem>神勢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>之化。化諸梵志。
<lb n="0550b25"/>斯等內外<note n="0550032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】＊</note><note n="0550032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0550032"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>淨。猶若新&CB00626;易可為色。唯願
<lb n="0550b26"/><note n="0550033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝天【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550033"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>尊。蕩其微垢。令成真淨。梵志見佛。心開
<lb n="0550b27"/>意喜。皆作沙門。佛<note n="0550034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝告諸比丘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝告諸比丘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550034"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">告諸比丘</rdg></app>我為汝曹說經。上語
<lb n="0550b28"/>亦善。中語亦善。下語亦善。語中深說度世之
<lb n="0550b29"/>道。<note n="0550035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">政＝正【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">政＝正【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550035"><lem>政</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">正</rdg></app>心為本。聽我所言。使後世傳行之。諸
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0743.0550c" n="0550c"/>
<lb n="0550c01"/>比丘皆叉手受教。佛言人身<note n="0550036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550036"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。有五賊。牽
<lb n="0550c02"/>人入惡道。何等為五。一者色。二者痛<note n="0550037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痒＝癢【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0550037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痒＝癢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0550037"><lem>痒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">癢</rdg></app>。三
<lb n="0550c03"/>者思想。四者生死。五者識是五者。人所常念。
<lb n="0550c04"/>佛言<note n="0550038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＋（身）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人＋（身）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550038"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人身</rdg></app>常為目所欺。為耳所欺。為鼻所欺。
<lb n="0550c05"/>為口所欺。<note n="0550039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為身所欺〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為身所欺〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550039"><lem>為身所欺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。目但能見不能<note n="0550040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞＝聽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞＝聽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550040"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聽</rdg></app>。耳
<lb n="0550c06"/>但能聞不能見。鼻但能知<note n="0550041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香臭＝臭香【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香臭＝臭香【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550041"><lem>香臭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臭香</rdg></app>不能<note n="0550042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知味＝聞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">知味＝聞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550042"><lem>知味</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聞</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0550c07"/>口但能知味不能知香臭。身<note n="0550043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔體〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔體〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550043"><lem>體</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>但能知寒溫
<lb n="0550c08"/>不能知味。<note n="0550044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550044"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>五者皆屬心。心為本。佛<note n="0550045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝告【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝告【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550045"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">告</rdg></app>諸
<lb n="0550c09"/>比丘。欲求道者。當端汝心。人從癡故。隨十二
<lb n="0550c10"/>因緣。便有生死。何等為十二<note n="0550046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔因緣〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔因緣〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550046"><lem>因緣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。一者<note n="0550047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癡＋（本為）【三】</note><note n="0550047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癡＋（本為）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0550047"><lem>癡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">癡本為</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0550c11"/>二者行。三者識。四者名色。五者六入。六者
<lb n="0550c12"/><note n="0550048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">栽＝觸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">栽＝觸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550048"><lem>栽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">觸</rdg></app>。七者痛。八者愛。九者<note n="0550049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝取【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受＝取【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550049"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>。十者有。十一
<lb n="0550c13"/>者生。十二者死。施行善者。復得為人。施行
<lb n="0550c14"/>惡者入<note n="0550050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地獄＝泥犁【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0550050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">地獄＝泥犁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0550050"><lem>地獄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">泥犁</rdg></app><note n="0550051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼＝薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼＝薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550051"><lem>餓鬼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">薜荔</rdg></app>畜生鬼神中。佛坐思念。
<lb n="0550c15"/>人癡故<note n="0550052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（便）＋有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（便）＋有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550052"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便有</rdg></app>生死。何等為癡本。從癡中來。今
<lb n="0550c16"/>生為人。復癡心不解。目不開。不知死<note n="0550053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當何趣＝趣何道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當何趣＝趣何道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550053"><lem>當何
<lb n="0550c17"/>趣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">趣何道</rdg></app>。見佛不問。見經不讀。見沙門不承事。不信
<lb n="0550c18"/>道德。見父母不敬。不念世間苦。不知<anchor id="fxT17p0550c01"/>地獄
<lb n="0550c19"/>中<note n="0550054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">考＝拷【元】</note><app n="0550054"><lem>考</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">拷</rdg></app>治劇。是名為癡。故有生死不<note n="0550055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">止人＝息人生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0550055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止人＝息人生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0550055"><lem>止。人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">息人生</rdg></app>死
<lb n="0550c20"/>如呼吸之間。脆不過於人命。人身中有三事。
<lb n="0550c21"/>身死識去。心去意去。是三者。常相追逐。施行
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0743.0551a" n="0551a"/>
<lb n="0551a01"/>惡者。入<anchor id="fxT17p0551a01"/>地獄<note n="0551001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼＝禽獸薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼＝禽獸薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551001"><lem>餓鬼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">禽獸薜荔</rdg></app>畜生鬼神中。施行善者。
<lb n="0551a02"/>三亦相追逐。或生天上。或生人中。墮是五道
<lb n="0551a03"/>中者。皆坐心不端故。佛告諸比丘。皆當端汝
<lb n="0551a04"/>目。端汝耳。端汝鼻。端汝口。端汝身。端汝心。
<lb n="0551a05"/>身體皆當斷於土。魂神當不復<note n="0551002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墮＝入【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墮＝入【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551002"><lem>墮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app><note n="0551003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">泥犁＋（薛荔）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥犁＋（薛荔）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551003"><lem>泥犁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">泥犁薛荔</rdg></app>畜
<lb n="0551a06"/>生鬼神中。視人家有惡子。為吏所取。皆坐心
<lb n="0551a07"/>不端故。人身中有百字。如車有百<note n="0551004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝人【宮】</note><app n="0551004"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>。人多
<lb n="0551a08"/>貪好怒。不思惟身中事。死<note n="0551005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝墮【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入＝墮【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551005"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">墮</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT17p0551a02"/>地獄中。後
<lb n="0551a09"/><note n="0551006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悔＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悔＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551006"><lem>悔</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悔之</rdg></app>無所復及。我棄國捐<note n="0551007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉輪＝遮迦越【三】，遮迦曰【宮】</note><note n="0551007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉輪＝遮迦越【宋】【元】【明】，＝遮迦曰【宮】</note><app n="0551007"><lem>轉輪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">遮迦越</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">遮迦曰</rdg></app>王。憂斷生死。
<lb n="0551a10"/>欲<note n="0551008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">度＝使【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">度＝使【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551008"><lem>度</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>世間人<note n="0551009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔使〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔使〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551009"><lem>使</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得<note n="0551010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無為＝泥洹【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無為＝泥洹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551010"><lem>無為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">泥洹</rdg></app>道。第一精進者。立
<lb n="0551a11"/>得阿羅漢。第二精進者。得阿那含。第三精進
<lb n="0551a12"/>者。得斯陀含。第四精進者。得須陀洹。雖不能
<lb n="0551a13"/>大精進。當持五戒。不殺不盜不婬不<note n="0551011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兩舌＝欺【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩舌＝欺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551011"><lem>兩舌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">欺</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0551a14"/>飲酒</p>
<lb n="0551a15"/><p>佛言。人坐起常當思念四事。何等四。一者自
<lb n="0551a16"/>觀<note n="0551012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（人）＋身【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（人）＋身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551012"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人身</rdg></app>。觀他人身。二者自觀痛<anchor id="fxT17p0551a03"/>痒。觀他人痛
<lb n="0551a17"/><anchor id="fxT17p0551a04"/>痒。三者自觀意。觀他人意。四者自觀法。觀
<lb n="0551a18"/>他人法。<note n="0551013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內復欲亂者心＝心小欲亂意【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內復欲亂者心＝心小欲亂意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551013"><lem>內復欲亂者心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心小欲亂意</rdg></app>當自端視<anchor id="fxT17p0551a05"/>身體。<note n="0551014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飢＝飽【三】，胞【宮】</note><note n="0551014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飢＝飽【宋】【元】【明】，＝胞【宮】</note><app n="0551014"><lem>飢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飽</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">胞</rdg></app>
<lb n="0551a19"/>亦極。<note n="0551015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飽＝飢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飽＝飢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551015"><lem>飽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飢</rdg></app>亦極。<note n="0551016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝住【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551016"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>亦極。<note n="0551017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝行【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551017"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>亦極。<note n="0551018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坐＝寒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">坐＝寒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551018"><lem>坐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">寒</rdg></app>亦極。
<lb n="0551a20"/><note n="0551019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寒＝熱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寒＝熱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551019"><lem>寒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">熱</rdg></app>亦極。<note n="0551020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熱＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熱＝臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551020"><lem>熱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臥</rdg></app>亦極。臥欲來時。當自驚起坐端
<lb n="0551a21"/>心坐。心不端者。當起立。立不端者。當經行。心
<lb n="0551a22"/>儻不端者。當自<note n="0551021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝政【宮】</note><app n="0551021"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">政</rdg></app>。譬如<note n="0551022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋國【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（有）＋國【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551022"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">有國</rdg></app>王將兵出&CB00508;。健
<lb n="0551a23"/>者在前。既在前<note n="0551023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄙＝圖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鄙＝圖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551023"><lem>鄙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">圖</rdg></app>復&CB00230;<note n="0551024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適＝退【宋】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551024"><lem>適</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">退</rdg></app>欲&CB00230;<note n="0551025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">著＝養【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0551025"><lem>著</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">養</rdg></app><note n="0551026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羞〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔羞〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551026"><lem>羞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>後
<lb n="0551a24"/>人。<note n="0551027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551027"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘既棄家<note n="0551028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">捨＝捐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捨＝捐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551028"><lem>捨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">捐</rdg></app>妻子。剃<note n="0551029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬚髮＝頭鬚【宮】</note><app n="0551029"><lem>鬚髮</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">頭鬚</rdg></app>為沙
<lb n="0551a25"/>門。雖一世<note n="0551030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔勤〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔勤〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551030"><lem>勤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>苦。後長解脫。<anchor id="fxT17p0551a06"/>已得道者。內
<lb n="0551a26"/><note n="0551031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獨＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獨＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551031"><lem>獨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg></app><note n="0551032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歡喜＝觀【宮】</note><app n="0551032"><lem>歡喜</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app>。視妻如<note n="0551033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（視）＋姊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（視）＋姊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551033"><lem>姊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">視姊</rdg></app>弟。視子如知識。無貪
<lb n="0551a27"/>愛之心。常當慈哀十方諸天人民。<anchor id="fxT17p0551a07"/>地獄<note n="0551034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">餓鬼畜生＝禽獸薜荔【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">餓鬼畜生＝禽獸薜荔【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551034"><lem>餓
<lb n="0551a28"/>鬼畜生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">禽獸薜荔</rdg></app>蜎飛蠕動之類。皆使富貴<note n="0551035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安隱度脫＝壽樂【宮】</note><app n="0551035"><lem>安隱度
<lb n="0551a29"/>脫</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">壽樂</rdg></app>。得<anchor id="fxT17p0551a08"/>無為之道。見<note n="0551036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝&CB13428;【宋】【宮】，畋【元】【明】</note><note n="0551036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲＝&CB13428;【宋】【宮】，＝畋【元】【明】</note><app n="0551036"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB13428;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">畋</rdg></app><note n="0551037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獸＝獵【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獸＝獵【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551037"><lem>獸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">獵</rdg></app>當以慈<note n="0551038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哀愍傷＝心傷哀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哀愍傷＝心傷哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551038"><lem>哀愍傷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心傷哀</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0743.0551b" n="0551b"/>
<lb n="0551b01"/>之知生不復癡。能有是意者。常念師恩。事佛
<lb n="0551b02"/>如人念父母。如獄中<note n="0551039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋死【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（有）＋死【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551039"><lem>死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">有死</rdg></app>罪囚。有賢者往請囚
<lb n="0551b03"/>出囚。黠慧者常念賢者恩。比丘<anchor id="fxT17p0551b01"/>已得道者。
<lb n="0551b04"/>當念佛。如是念經。當如人念<note n="0551040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲＝飯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551040"><lem>飲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>食。諸比丘。
<lb n="0551b05"/>當<note n="0551041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔轉〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔轉〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551041"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>相承事。如弟事兄。中有癡者。當問黠
<lb n="0551b06"/>者。展轉相教。問黠者如瞑中有燈火。無得陰
<lb n="0551b07"/>謀。作惡無得諍訟。見金銀當如見<note n="0551042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（糞）＋土【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（糞）＋土【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551042"><lem>土</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">糞土</rdg></app>。無得
<lb n="0551b08"/>妄證<note n="0551043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人入＝入人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人入＝入人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551043"><lem>人入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">入人</rdg></app>罪法。<note n="0551044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語言＝言語【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語言＝言語【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551044"><lem>語言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">言語</rdg></app>無得<note n="0551045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妄〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔妄〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551045"><lem>妄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>中傷人意。不
<lb n="0551b09"/><note n="0551046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞＝見【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聞＝見【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551046"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>莫言<anchor id="fxT17p0551b02"/>聞。不<note n="0551047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝聞【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝聞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551047"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聞</rdg></app>莫言<anchor id="fxT17p0551b03"/>見。行道<note n="0551048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（常）＋當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（常）＋當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551048"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">常當</rdg></app>低頭視
<lb n="0551b10"/>地蟲。無得蹈殺。無得<note n="0551049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">目＝自【元】，〔目〕－【明】</note><app n="0551049"><lem>目</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>貪人婦女。無得形
<lb n="0551b11"/>相人婦女。坐自思惟。去<note n="0551050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貪愛＝愛貪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貪愛＝愛貪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551050"><lem>貪愛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">愛貪</rdg></app>之心。乃得<note n="0551051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551051"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0551b12"/>道耳</p>
<lb n="0551b13"/><p>佛告諸比丘。欲求道者。當<note n="0551052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔端汝心〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551052"><lem>端汝心</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。於閑處
<lb n="0551b14"/>坐。自呼吸其氣息。知息短長。長息不報。形
<lb n="0551b15"/>體亦極。閉氣不息。形體亦極。分別<note n="0551053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（自）＋思惟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（自）＋思惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551053"><lem>思惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自思惟</rdg></app>。形
<lb n="0551b16"/>體誰作者。心當<note n="0551054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視內＝觀外【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視內＝觀外【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551054"><lem>視內</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">觀外</rdg></app>。亦當觀<note n="0551055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">外＝內【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＝內【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551055"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">內</rdg></app>。自思惟歡
<lb n="0551b17"/>然與人有。異心。當是時不用天下珍寶。心稍
<lb n="0551b18"/>欲隨正道。意復小動者。即還自守其意。意即
<lb n="0551b19"/>為還。譬如人有鏡。鏡不明<note n="0551056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔則〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔則〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551056"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不見其形。磨
<lb n="0551b20"/>去其垢。<note n="0551057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝即【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝即【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551057"><lem>乃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>自見<note n="0551058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝譬如【宮】</note><app n="0551058"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">譬如</rdg></app>。人<note n="0551059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔以〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551059"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>去貪婬<note n="0551060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（去）＋瞋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（去）＋瞋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551060"><lem>瞋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">去瞋</rdg></app>恚<note n="0551061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（去）＋愚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（去）＋愚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551061"><lem>愚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">去愚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0551b21"/>癡。<note n="0551062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譬如磨鏡〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551062"><lem>譬如磨鏡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0551063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">端自＝諦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">端自＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551063"><lem>端自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諦</rdg></app>思惟。天下無堅固。皆
<lb n="0551b22"/><note n="0551064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無有＝有無【三】</note><note n="0551064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無有＝有無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0551064"><lem>無有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">有無</rdg></app>常</p>
<lb n="0551b23"/><p>佛告諸比丘。持心當如四方石。石在中。庭雨
<lb n="0551b24"/><note n="0551065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔墮〕－【宮】</note><app n="0551065"><lem>墮</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0551066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551066"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亦不</rdg></app>能壞。日炎亦不能<note n="0551067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消＝銷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551067"><lem>消</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">銷</rdg></app>。風吹亦不能
<lb n="0551b25"/><note n="0551068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＝起【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">動＝起【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551068"><lem>動</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">起</rdg></app>持心當如石。<note n="0551069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛言〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛言〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551069"><lem>佛言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>天下人心。如流水中
<lb n="0551b26"/><note n="0551070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551070"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>草木。各自流行。不相顧望。前者亦不顧
<lb n="0551b27"/>後。後者亦不顧前。草木流行。各自如故。人心
<lb n="0551b28"/>亦如是。一念來一念去。亦如草木前後不相
<lb n="0551b29"/><note n="0551071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顧＝須【宋】</note><app n="0551071"><lem>顧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">須</rdg></app>望。於天上天下。無所復樂寄居。天地間
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0743.0551c" n="0551c"/>
<lb n="0551c01"/>棄身不復死。道成乃<note n="0551072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（能）＋知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（能）＋知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551072"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">能知</rdg></app>師恩。見師即承事。
<lb n="0551c02"/>不見者思惟其教誡。如孝子念父母。<note n="0551073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意定乃有一心＝如人念飯食道定【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551073" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意定乃有一心＝如人念飯食道定【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551073"><lem>意定乃
<lb n="0551c03"/>有一心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">如人念飯食道定</rdg></app>。<note n="0551074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＋（更）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551074" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＋（更）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551074"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便更</rdg></app>慈哀天下人民<note n="0551075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜎飛蠕動之類坐獨自歎已＝虫蛾六畜坐獨自笑以【宮】</note><app n="0551075"><lem>蜎飛蠕動之類。
<lb n="0551c04"/>坐獨自歎已</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">虫蛾六畜坐獨自笑以</rdg></app>脫身於天下及五道。一者天道。
<lb n="0551c05"/>二者人道。三者畜<note n="0551076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＋（虫蛾）【宮】</note><app n="0551076"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">生虫蛾</rdg></app>道。四者餓鬼道。五者
<lb n="0551c06"/><anchor id="fxT17p0551c01"/>地獄道。<note n="0551077" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已得羅漢道＝為羅漢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551077" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已得羅漢道＝為羅漢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551077"><lem>已得羅漢道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">為羅漢</rdg></app>者。<note n="0551078" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝即【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551078" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝即【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551078"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">即</rdg></app>能飛行<note n="0551079" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">變＝戀【宋】，〔變化〕－【宮】</note><note n="0551079" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔變化〕－【宮】，變＝戀【宋】</note><app n="0551079"><lem>變化</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">戀化</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0551c07"/>身中<note n="0551080" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔能〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0551080" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔能〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0551080"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>出水火。<anchor id="fxT17p0551c02"/>能出無間入無孔。欲離世
<lb n="0551c08"/>間。取<anchor id="fxT17p0551c03"/>無為去者即能</p>
<lb n="0551c09"/><p>佛告諸比丘。道不可不學。經不可不讀。佛說
<lb n="0551c10"/>經已。五百沙門。皆得阿羅漢道。阿難白佛言。
<lb n="0551c11"/>是諸沙門。聞經意解。何其疾也。佛言。此諸比
<lb n="0551c12"/>丘前迦葉佛時。受誦斯經。中間無佛。隨世因
<lb n="0551c13"/>緣廢不復聞。至<note n="0551081" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今）＋吾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0551081" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今）＋吾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0551081"><lem>吾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">今吾</rdg></app>為說。聞即得道。佛說經
<lb n="0551c14"/>竟。諸菩薩。四輩弟子。帝王人民。天龍鬼神。
<lb n="0551c15"/>無不歡喜。為佛作禮</p>
<lb n="0551c16"/><trailer><title>佛說<anchor id="fxT17p0551c04"/>忠心經</title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
